prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D illustration for a greeting card front. A humorous and vibrant beach scene celebrating a birthday, rendered in a beautiful botanical art style.

The scene features cartoon versions of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo, full-body, standing on a sandy beach. Lao Lao, on the left, is wearing her blue sweatshirt and black pants. She has a huge, exaggerated, happy smile and is holding a giant, oversized coconut drink with a tiny umbrella and a silly straw. Jordan, wearing his tan hoodie and dark pants, is standing behind her, playfully attempting to build a sandcastle on top of her head with a small bucket and shovel, looking mischievous but loving.

The background is a stylized, sunny beach with gentle, stylized waves. Instead of typical palm trees, the beach is whimsically framed by an arch of lush, botanical elements like oversized monstera leaves, tropical ferns, and vibrant hibiscus flowers, blending the botanical and beach themes. A few cartoon crabs wearing tiny party hats are scattered on the sand.

Floating in the center of the image, slightly above the couple, is the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao" in a beautiful, readable, handwritten cursive script. The color palette is bright and cheerful, with soft pastel tones for the sky and water, and vibrant greens and floral colors for the botanical frame. The overall composition is joyful, quirky, and full of personality.
